DESCRIPTION:For more than 40 years\, outdoor enthusiasts have turned to To
 m Stienstra for guidance on the best waterfalls\, unforgettable campsites\
 , and hidden wild places. A longtime outdoors writer and editor for the Sa
 n Francisco Chronicle and KCBS-FM\, Stienstra is also the bestselling auth
 or of essential guidebooks like Moon’s California Camping and 52 Weekend
  Adventures in Northern California.\n\nMore info & tickets: https://www.co
 mmonwealthclub.org/events/2026-05-26/outdoors-writer-tom-stienstra-shares-
 his-tales-survival-and-top-adventure-spots
