DESCRIPTION:Nowhere is the dual threat of climate change and geopolitical 
 competition felt more strongly than in the Arctic. Sea ice is declining ra
 pidly\, wildfires are burning\, and permafrost is thawing. At the same tim
 e\, global interest is growing rapidly as the region transforms from being
  a frozen desert into an international waterway.\n\nMore info & tickets: h
 ttps://www.commonwealthclub.org/events/2026-06-08/unfrozen-fight-future-ar
