BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Kama Sutra for Senior Citizens\, and Other Poems on Aging
DTSTART:20260625T003000Z
DTEND:20260625T023000Z
DTSTAMP:20260524T214200Z
UID:04d4f509-8382-5416-9afa-ed6dffe8569a
DESCRIPTION:Please join Zack Rogow\, in conversation with Steven Winn of C
 ity Arts & Lectures\, as they discuss and Zack reads from his new book of 
 poems\, about seeking love later in life. It is also about the process of 
 aging and how that changes us both physically and emotionally. The poems d
 eal with what is lost as we get older\, but also the accumulated experienc
 e that helps us connect better with our loved ones. When he became single 
 at age 66\, he was inspired to write about what we all long for: connectio
 n and passion.\n\nMore info & tickets: https://www.commonwealthclub.org/ev
 ents/2026-06-24/kama-sutra-senior-citizens-and-other-poems-aging
