DTEND:20260625T030000Z
DTSTAMP:20260524T214200Z
UID:4c522a92-cf42-5b4d-bc5c-56b0a27a4494
DESCRIPTION:In a recent essay\, President George W. Bush hails George Wash
 ington’s decision to leave the presidency after two terms\, ensuring Ame
 rica would not become a monarchy. “[His] humility in giving up power wil
 lingly remains among the most consequential decisions and important exampl
 es in American politics.”\n\nMore info & tickets: https://www.commonweal
