SUMMARY:Regime Change: Everything You Need to Know
DTSTART:20260625T013000Z
DTEND:20260625T033000Z
DTSTAMP:20260524T214200Z
UID:71aebb62-64f8-5da2-837a-ef8a3f60529f
DESCRIPTION:Venezuela\, Iran and Ukraine are only the latest in a long str
 ing of what have become known as interventions for regime change. But wher
 e did this idea come from\, and when did it become an option in the strate
 gic arsenal of global politics? \nThere are plenty of questions to be ask
 ed and answered about its legality and about its effectiveness\, and we wi
 ll go through each of those questions one by one during this talk.\nAbout 
 the Speaker \n\nMore info & tickets: https://www.commonwealthclub.org/eve
 nts/2026-06-24/regime-change-everything-you-need-know
