UID:b6bb0ec4-541f-5b56-8b25-3d2f4b873dea
DESCRIPTION:Some rooms change you. This will be one of them. Join us for R
 esistance In Action at SF Pride’s 4th Annual Human Rights Summit.\nLeade
 rs. Activists. Revolutionaries. Visionaries. Legends. Icons. Truth seekers
 . Freedom fighters. Rebels. Innovators. Dreamers. If you care about our co
 llective future\, this room was built for you to dive deeply into what it 
 means to be free\, liberated and safe.\nKeynote speaker: Dolores Huerta\n\
 nMore info & tickets: https://www.commonwealthclub.org/events/2026-06-25/s
 an-francisco-pride-fourth-annual-human-rights-summit
