BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Trans Ironmen
DTSTART:20260629T230000Z
DTEND:20260630T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260524T214200Z
UID:2537987d-8d4d-50d2-a905-f0a1a1881988
DESCRIPTION:Amidst a backdrop of unprecedented attacks on trans athletes\,
  Schuyler\, Chella\, and Cal teamed up to take on the Ironman 70.3 relay i
 n Oceanside\, California\, together on March 28\, 2026—placing third in 
 the men’s relay category. Schuyler in the water\, Chella on wheels\, and
  Cal hitting the pavement\, these trans masculine athletes defy the erasur
 e so commonly perpetuated against them\, leaning into movement as essentia
 l empowerment\, teamwork as vital community\, and self-love as fuel. \n\n
 More info & tickets: https://www.commonwealthclub.org/events/2026-06-29/tr
 ans-ironmen
LOCATION:The Commonwealth Club of California\, Taube Family Auditorium\, S
 an Francisco\, CA
URL:https://www.commonwealthclub.org/events/2026-06-29/trans-ironmen
