DTEND:20260709T030000Z
DTSTAMP:20260524T214200Z
UID:8fb0cd41-6364-5187-80a5-3ea8c625c98a
DESCRIPTION:The U.S. Constitution is often at the center of debates about 
 rights and wrongs and public policies in this country\, but how many peopl
 e have actually read it? How many have thought about it? How many understa
 nd it?\n\nMore info & tickets: https://www.commonwealthclub.org/events/202
 6-07-08/melissa-murray-understanding-us-constitution
