 ind the Declaration of Independence and how its message was shared in 1776
 .\nDrawing on her latest research\, Dr Sneff will explore how news of inde
 pendence spread across the colonies and beyond\, offering fresh insights i
 nto this pivotal moment in American history. This in-person event provides
