 ian Nationalism
DTSTART:20260819T010000Z
DTEND:20260819T030000Z
DTSTAMP:20260524T214200Z
UID:6687a73f-ad51-59fc-a48a-41690c962ffd
DESCRIPTION:Sinclair Lewis is said to have predicted\, “When fascism com
 es to America\, it will be wrapped in the flag and carrying the cross.” 
 Democratic congressman Jared Huffman says he witnessed something eerily li
 ke that vision on January 6\, 2021\, and it was his wake-up call to the sh
 ocking power of Christian nationalism.\n\nMore info & tickets: https://www
 .commonwealthclub.org/events/2026-08-18/congressman-jared-huffman-fight-sa
